description:
## Fish Bone Family Bar & Restaurant: A Taste of Goa in Sancaole

Nestled in the heart of Goa Velha, Fish Bone Family Bar & Restaurant, formerly known as Sawmill Cafe, invites diners into a culinary experience that, although recently transitioned in name and management, holds a 3.7-star rating from a considerable 706 reviews. Patrons from all walks of life traverse here for predominantly Goan dishes, with a special fondness for their thali offerings. Notably, tags frequently associated with the restaurant include "service" (41 mentions), "thali" (17 mentions), "experience" (16 mentions), and "Goan" (14 mentions), hinting at both the local essence of the cuisine and the restaurant‚Äôs service strength.

### Ambiance & Design 

As you approach Fish Bone, the exterior presents a somewhat unassuming fa√ßade but fosters curiosity about what lies within. Entering, patrons are greeted by a spacious ambiance that's both relaxed and inviting, mostly noted positively in customer reviews. The lighting softly illuminates the space, enhancing its casual charm, while customer-generated images showcase neat table setups and ample seating options‚Äîideal for both families and groups of friends. However, there are whispers of the need for better maintenance, particularly concerning cleanliness in the restrooms, which received mixed feedback regarding upkeep.

### Menu & Culinary Experience

While the menu is lauded for including tasty Goan fare, the quality of the food experiences some divide among those who have dined here. Signature dishes center around thali presentations, which many reviewers appreciated for their flavor and presentation; however, equality in this aspect seems to fluctuate, with some describing the food as merely "good" but not "great." Notably, the cutlery's condition has drawn some critiquing eyes, prompting a call for improvement that could mirror the dining quality expected at such a picturesque location.

The menu's layout was a point of contention, with one reviewer expressing disappointment over the absence of a drink menu, suggesting a need for clearer communication of offerings to enhance the dining experience. Dietary options and specialty dietary needs were not highlighted, indicating potential room for expansion in this area.

### Customer Experience & Service

Service at Fish Bone Family Bar & Restaurant garners a mixed bag of reviews. Many customers acknowledged the staff's training in being polite and helpful, contributing positively to the overall dining experience. However, there were instances suggesting the staff wasn‚Äôt as welcoming as desired, hinting at inconsistency in hospitality that the establishment might want to address to forge a stronger connection with its clientele. Management changes appear to have positively impacted the kitchen staff, as regulars reported an uplift in food quality following those transitions.

### Popularity & Reviews

The overall sentiment among diners appears to lean towards cautious optimism, as many commented on the improved culinary offerings since its rebranding. Social media buzz mentions of better food management resonate well, contributing to a steadily increasing reputation among local patrons. Suggestions for improvement focus primarily on the cleaning of facilities, menu clarity, and consistency in service, which could elevate the establishment from a "nice place" to one that is truly memorable.

### Utilizing Visual Content

Customer-provided images bring life to the restaurant's offerings, showcasing vibrant thali presentations that stir appetites and decorated interiors that hint at the comforting atmosphere. The spacious layout captured in photographs underscores the ideal dining setting for both intimate meals and larger gatherings. However, there is an underlying message in some images that call for refinement in the details of food presentation and tableware.

In conclusion, Fish Bone Family Bar & Restaurant offers a commendable dining experience filled with the flavors of Goa, but it certainly has a path to travel toward achieving its fullest potential. With some attention to ambiance maintenance, food consistency, and a more engaging service style, it could become a destination of unequivocal note within the culinary landscape of Goa.
